'Kalung ini milik era Peshwa.'

00:20:13.360 --> 00:20:14.960 line:20%
“Itu sangat penting.”

00:20:17.400 --> 00:20:18.680 line:20%
'Lemari nenek
dibiarkan terbuka.'

00:20:18.760 --> 00:20:19.920 line:20%
“Kuharap tidak terjadi apa-apa.”

00:20:24.440 --> 00:20:25.840 line:20%
'Kemana perginya kalung itu?'

